Property Binding

<h4>{{recommended}}</h4>

<p>{{1+1}}</p>  1+1 is a template expression.
in property-binding, the template expression
appears in quotes after the "=" of a property.

<img [src]="itemImageUrl2">

property is "src" and it is equal to "itemImageUrl2"
which should be set in the class.

in template expressions you cannot have
javascript expressions that have side effects.
++, +- , new , instanceof, typeof, etc.
